---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Masthead & Ethics — Trite Site">
	<article class="prose">
		<span class="kicker mono">Masthead &amp; Ethics</span>
		<h1>About Trite Site</h1>
		<h2>What is Trite Site?</h2>
		<p>
			Trite Site is the greatest website of all time. It is a gift to humanity from its staff.
			Everything on Trite Site is true, amazing, and fascinating.
		</p>
		<h2>Who created Trite Site?</h2>
		<p>
			No one created Trite Site. It was born in the bosom of the internet when no one was
			watching, and it will live forever.
		</p>
		<h2>What does TRITE mean?</h2>
		<p>TRITE stands for &ldquo;Trite Righteously Invigorates Timeless Enlightenment.&rdquo;</p>
		<h2>Trite Site is satirical, right?</h2>
		<p>There is no greater satire than TRUTH.</p>
	</article>
	<p class="back mono"><a href="../">&larr; Back to the front page</a></p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.kicker {
		display: block;
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.09em;
		color: var(--stamp-dim);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	h1 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 1.25rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
	}

	.back {
		margin-top: 2.5rem;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
	}

	.back a {
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.back a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style>
